No, the release version of Balloon Fight uses a NROM-128 board.  The ROM size should be 24KB (16KB PRG + 8KB CHR.)  NROM-256 boards produce 40KB ROMS (32KB PRG + 8KB CHR.)<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=58">Great Hierophant</a> — Fri Apr 28, 2006 9:43 am</p><hr />
